{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782366062067,"sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_uTfsD9y1cIZv70C9H2LvxFjI","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\current-agent-input.md","limit":400},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\current-agent-input.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Agent Input Brief - phase-03-onboarding-login-profile / phase\n2: \n3: This brief is a narrow planning input compiled from current workflow reports. It is not an authority file.\n4: Start here, then open only the referenced source paths, target endpoints, capabilities, or reports needed for the task.\n5: \n6: ## Boundaries\n7: \n8: - Source project: `D:\\Kotlin2Cangjie\\Foodike`\n9: - Target project: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony`\n10: - Translation inputs: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs`\n11: - Do not read sibling old translations unless the user explicitly asks for comparison.\n12: - Edit only target project files and agent-maintained authority files required by the current session.\n13: \n14: ## Freshness\n15: \n16: | artifact | exists | generatedAt | phase | error |\n17: | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n18: | phaseTaskChecklist | yes | 2026-06-25T05:40:29+00:00 | phase-03-onboarding-login-profile |  |\n19: | phaseGroupVerdicts | yes | 2026-06-25T05:40:13+00:00 | phase-02-startup-navigation-session |  |\n20: | phaseCapabilityChecklist | yes | 2026-06-25T05:40:30+00:00 | phase-03-onboarding-login-profile |  |\n21: | translationQualitySummary | no |  |  | missing |\n22: | phaseCoverageGate | yes | 2026-06-25T05:40:15+00:00 | phase-02-startup-navigation-session |  |\n23: | targetStructure | yes | 2026-06-25T05:40:29+00:00 |  |  |\n24: | sourceCoverageMatrix | yes | 2026-06-25T02:01:25+00:00 |  |  |\n25: | platformCapabilityCheck | yes | 2026-06-25T02:01:25+00:00 |  |  |\n26: \n27: ## Scope Rules\n2