{"type":"text","timestamp":1782366090682,"sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","part":{"id":"prt_efd4c2ba7001kqE2CnMjmD3u1g","messageID":"msg_efd4bc9f5001LKO38nMdExk69o","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","type":"text","text":"Scope is confirmed: no unresolved platform capabilities for this phase, but all onboarding/login/profile feature rows are still open and need precise endpoint evidence. Next I’m inspecting the source screens and the current Harmony target structure to implement the missing flows against existing app/session foundations.","time":{"start":1782366088103,"end":1782366090681}}}
