Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\state_management\\cj-appstorage\\AppStorage应用全局的UI状态存储\\使用场景\\不建议借助StorageLink的双向同步机制实现事件通知.md:\n  Line 40:                 ForEach(this.dataList, itemGeneratorFunc: {item : ViewData , idx : Int64 =>\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-lazyforeach\\LazyForEach数据懒加载\\附件.md:\n  Line 10:     public BasicDataSource(let data_: ArrayList<T>) {}\r\n\n  Line 11:     public var listenerOp: ArrayList<DataChangeListener> = ArrayList<DataChangeListener>()\r\n\n  Line 21:         for (listeneritem in listenerOp) {\r\n\n  Line 44:         for (listeneritem in listenerOp) {\r\n\n  Line 51:         for (listeneritem in listenerOp) {\r\n\n  Line 58:         for (listeneritem in listenerOp) {\r\n\n  Line 65:         for (listeneritem in listenerOp) {\r\n\n  Line 72:         for (listeneritem in listenerOp) {\r\n\n  Line 77:     public func notifyDatasetChange(operations: ArrayList<DataOperation>): Unit {\r\n\n  Line 78:         for (listeneritem in listenerOp) {\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-lazyforeach\\LazyForEach数据懒加载\\组件创建规则\\首次渲染.md:\n  Line 13:     public MyDataSource(let data: ArrayList<String>) {\r\n\n  Line 21:     let dataSource: MyDataSource = MyDataSource(ArrayList<String>())\r\n\n  Line 26:         for (i in 0..100) {\r\n\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 362 matches (262 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":362,"truncated":true},"title":"ArrayList<|for \\(|ForEach\\(|LazyForEach\\(","time":{"start":1782366278620,"end":1782366278827}},"id":"prt_efd4f13860017H2stLaThANGh1","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","messageID":"msg_efd4e7dc5001zTJipaWDXVuxtI"}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1782366279107,"sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","part":{"id":"prt_efd4f15c1001L4ARegRIFaiy2R","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"9d8e211084bd2695382a11debfc5278d43829dae","messageID":"msg_efd4e7dc5001zTJipaWDXVuxtI","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":137554,"input":78789,"output":195,"reasoning":586,"cache":{"write":0,"read":57984}},"cost":0}}
