{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782366297669,"sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_wftgbWD5v0ebV1YNIx0qCR4b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\state_management\\cj-state-management-best-practices\\状态管理优秀实践\\状态管理优秀实践_2more_036f9e32.md","limit":170},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\state_management\\cj-state-management-best-practices\\状态管理优秀实践\\状态管理优秀实践_2more_036f9e32.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 状态管理优秀实践\n2: \n3: <!--Del-->\n4: > **说明：**\n5: >\n6: > 当前为Beta阶段。\n7: <!--DelEnd-->\n8: \n9: 为了帮助应用程序开发人员提高其应用程序质量，特别是在高效的状态管理方面。本章节面向开发者提供了多个在开发ArkUI应用中常见的低效开发的场景，并给出了对应的解决方案。此外，还提供了同一场景下，推荐用法和不推荐用法的对比和解释说明，更直观地展示两者区别，从而帮助开发者学习如何正确地在应用开发中使用状态变量，进行高性能开发。\n10: \n11: ## 不使用状态变量强行更新非状态变量关联组件\n12: \n13: 【反例】\n14: \n15:  <!-- run -->\n16: \n17: ```cangjie\n18: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n19: \n20: import kit.ArkUI.*\n21: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n22: import kit.LocalizationKit.*\n23: import std.collection.*\n24: import kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n25: \n26: @Entry\n27: @Component\n28: class EntryView{\n29:     @State var needsUpdate: Bool = true\n30:     var realStateArr: ArrayList<Int64> = ArrayList<Int64>([4, 1, 3, 2])\n31:     var realState: Color = Color(0xFFFF00)\n32: \n33:     func updateUIArr(param: ArrayList<Int64>): ArrayList<Int64>{\n34:         let triggerAGet: Bool = this.needsUpdate\n35:         return param\n36:     }\n37: \n38:     func updateUI(param: Color): Color{\n39:         let triggerAGet: Bool = this.needsUpdate\n40:         return param\n41:     }\n42: \n43:     func build(){\n44:         Column(space: 20){\n45:             ForEach(this.updateUIArr(this.realStateArr), itemGeneratorFunc: {item: Int64, _: Int64 => Text(\"${item}\")})\n46:             Text(\"add item\")\n47:             .onClick({ event =>\n48:                 // 改变realStateArr不会触发UI视图更新\n49:                 this.realStateArr.add(this.realStateArr[this.realStateArr.size - 1] + 1)\n50: \n51:                 // 触发UI视图更新\n52:                 this.needsUpdate = !this.needsUpdate\n53:             })\n54: \n55:             Text(\"chg color\")\n56:             .onClick({event =>\n57:                 // 改变realState不会触发UI视图更新\n58:                 match {\n59:                     case this.realState.toUInt32() == Color(0xFFFF00).toUInt32() => this.realState = Color.Red\n60:                     case this.realState.toUInt32() == Color.Red.toUInt32() => this.realState = Color(0xFFFF00)\n61:                     case _ => Hilog.error(0, \"test\", \"realState invalid\")\n62:                 }\n63: \n64:                 // 触发UI视图更新\n65:                 this.needsUpdate = !this.needsUpdate\n66:             })\n67:         }\n68:         .backgroundColor(this.updateUI(this.realState))\n69:         .width(200).height(500)\n70:     }\n71: }\n72: ```\n73: \n74: 上述示例存在以下问题：\n75: \n76: - 应用程序希望控制UI更新逻辑，但在ArkUI中，UI更新的逻辑应该是由框架来检测应用程序状态变量的更改去实现。\n77: - this.needsUpdate是一个自定义的UI状态变量，应该仅应用于其绑定的UI组件。变量this.realStateArr、this.realState没有被装饰，其变化将不会触发UI刷新。\n78: - 但是在该应用中，用户试图通过this.needsUpdate的更新来带动常规变量this.realStateArr、this.realState的更新，此方法不合理且更新性能较差。\n79: \n80: 【正例】\n81: \n82: 要解决此问题，应将realStateArr和realState成员变量用@State装饰。一旦完成此操作，就不再需要变量needsUpdate。\n83: \n84:  <!-- run -->\n85: \n86: ```cangjie\n87: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n88: import kit.ArkUI.*\n89: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n90: import kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n91: \n92: @Entry\n93: @Component\n94: class EntryView{\n95:     @State var realStateArr: ObservedArrayList<Int64> = ObservedArrayList<Int64>([4, 1, 3, 2])\n96:     @State var realState: Color = Color(0xFFFF00)\n97: \n98:     func build(){\n99:         Column(space: 20){\n100:             ForEach(this.realStateArr, itemGeneratorFunc: {item: Int64, _: Int64 => Text(\"${item}\")})\n101: \n102:             Text(\"add item\")\n103:             .onClick({event =>\n104:                 // 改变realStateArr触发UI视图更新\n105:                 this.realStateArr.append((this.realStateArr[this.realStateArr.size - 1] + 1))\n106:             })\n107: \n108:             Text(\"chg color\")\n109:             .onClick({event =>\n110:                 // 改变realState触发UI视图更新\n111:                 match {\n112:                     case this.realState.toUInt32() == Color(0xFFFF00).toUInt32() => this.realState = Color.Red\n113:                     case this.realState.toUInt32() == Color.Red.toUInt32() => this.realState = Color(0xFFFF00)\n114:                     case _ => Hilog.error(0, \"test\", \"realState invalid\")\n115:                 }\n116:             })\n117:             .backgroundColor(this.realState)\n118:             .width(200).height(500)\n119:         }\n120:     }\n121: }\n122: ```\n\n(End of file - total 122 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 状态管理优秀实践\n\n<!--Del-->\n> **说明：**\n>\n> 当前为Beta阶段。\n<!--DelEnd-->\n\n为了帮助应用程序开发人员提高其应用程序质量，特别是在高效的状态管理方面。本章节面向开发者提供了多个在开发ArkUI应用中常见的低效开发的场景，并给出了对应的解决方案。此外，还提供了同一场景下，推荐用法和不推荐用法的对比和解释说明，更直观地展示两者区别，从而帮助开发者学习如何正确地在应用开发中使用状态变量，进行高性能开发。\n\n## 不使用状态变量强行更新非状态变量关联组件\n\n【反例】\n\n <!-- run -->\n\n```cangjie\npackage ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n\nimport kit.ArkUI.*","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\state_management\\cj-state-management-best-practices\\状态管理优秀实践\\状态管理优秀实践_2more_036f9e32.md","time":{"start":1782366297657,"end":1782366297668}},"id":"prt_efd4f5dc6001mO7DOYED0HRjhZ","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","messageID":"msg_efd4f16d4001SKgCELNFTYcv7p"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782366297761,"sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_zkLmFsyMmAKW4MrFV1GmNDFi","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-layout-development-create-looping\\创建轮播Swiper\\页面切换方式_3more_9dc4c044.md","limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-layout-development-create-looping\\创建轮播Swiper\\页面切换方式_3more_9dc4c044.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ## 页面切换方式\n2: \n3: Swiper支持手指滑动和点击导航点两种方式切换页面，以下示例展示通过控制器切换页面的方法。\n4: \n5:  <!-- run -->\n6: \n7: ```cangjie\n8: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n9: import kit.ArkUI.*\n10: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n11: \n12: @Entry\n13: @Component\n14: class EntryView {\n15:     private var swiperBackgroundColors: Array<Color> = [Color.Blue, Color.Black, Color.Gray, Color.Green, Color.White, Color.Red]\n16:     private var swiperController: SwiperController = SwiperController();\n17:     @State var animationModeStr: Bool = false\n18:     @State var targetIndex: Int64 = 0\n19:     func build() {\n20:         Column(space: 5) {\n21:             Swiper(controller: this.swiperController) {\n22:                 ForEach(\n23:                     this.swiperBackgroundColors,\n24:                     itemGeneratorFunc: {\n25:                         item: Color, index: Int64 => Text(index.toString())\n26:                             .width(250)\n27:                             .height(250)\n28:                             .backgroundColor(item)\n29:                             .textAlign(TextAlign.Center)\n30:                             .fontSize(30)\n31:                     }\n32:                 )\n33:             }\n34:             .indicator(true)\n35: \n36:             Row(space:12) {\n37:                 Button('showNext').onClick({\n38:                     evt => this\n39:                         .swiperController\n40:                         .showNext(); // 通过controller切换到后一页\n41:                 })\n42:                 Button('showPrevious').onClick({\n43:                     evt => this\n44:                         .swiperController\n45:                         .showPrevious(); // 通过controller切换到前一页\n46:                 })\n47:             }\n48:             .margin(5)\n49:             Row(space:12) {\n50:                 Text('Index:')\n51:                 Button(this.targetIndex.toString()).onClick(\n52:                     {\n53:                         evt => this.targetIndex = (this.targetIndex + 1) % this.swiperBackgroundColors.toArray().size\n54:                     })\n55:             }\n56:             .margin(5)\n57:             Row(space:12) {\n58:                 Text('AnimationMode:')\n59:                 Button(this.animationModeStr.toString()).onClick(\n60:                     {\n61:                         evt => if (this.animationModeStr == false) {\n62:                             this.animationModeStr = true\n63:                         } else {\n64:                             this.animationModeStr = false\n65:                         }\n66:                     })\n67:             }\n68:             .margin(5)\n69:         }\n70:         .width(100.percent)\n71:         .margin(top: 5)\n72:     }\n73: }\n74: ```\n75: \n76: ![controll](figures/controll.gif)\n77: \n78: ## 轮播方向\n79: \n80: Swiper支持水平和垂直方向上进行轮播，主要通过vertical属性控制。\n81: \n82: 当vertical为true时，表示在垂直方向上进行轮播；为false时，表示在水平方向上进行轮播。vertical默认值为false。\n83: \n84: - 设置水平方向上轮播。\n85: \n86:   ```cangjie\n87:   Swiper() {\n88:     // ...\n89:   }\n90:   .indicator(true)\n91:   .vertical(false)\n92:   ```\n93: \n94:   ![verticalFalse](figures/verticalFalse.PNG)\n95: \n96: - 设置垂直方向轮播。\n97: \n98:   ```cangjie\n99:   Swiper() {\n100:     // ...\n101:   }\n102:   .indicator(true)\n103:   .vertical(true)\n104:   ```\n105: \n106:   ![verticalTrue](figures/verticalTrue.PNG)\n107: \n108: ## 每页显示多个子页面\n109: \n110: Swiper支持在一个页面内同时显示多个子组件，通过[displayCount](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-scroll-swipe-swiper.md#func-displaycountint32-bool)属性设置。\n111: \n112:  <!-- run -->\n113: \n114: ```cangjie\n115: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n116: import kit.ArkUI.*\n117: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n118: \n119: @Entry\n120: @Component\n121: class EntryView {\n122:     func build() {\n123:         Column(space: 5) {\n124:               Swiper() {\n125:                   Text('0')\n126:                     .width(250)\n127:                     .height(250)\n128:                     .backgroundColor(Color.Gray)\n129:                     .textAlign(TextAlign.Center)\n130:                     .fontSize(30)\n131:                   Text('1')\n132:                     .width(250)\n133:                     .height(250)\n134:                     .backgroundColor(Color.Green)\n135:                     .textAlign(TextAlign.Center)\n136:                     .fontSize(30)\n137:                   Text('2')\n138:                     .width(250)\n139:                     .height(250)\n140:                     .backgroundColor(0xFEC0CD)\n141:                     .textAlign(TextAlign.Center)\n142:                     .fontSize(30)\n143:                   Text('3')\n144:                     .width(250)\n145:                     .height(250)\n146:                     .backgroundColor(Color.Blue)\n147:                     .textAlign(TextAlign.Center)\n148:                     .fontSize(30)\n149:                 }\n150:                 .indicator(true)\n151:                 .displayCount(2)\n152:         }\n153:         .width(100.percent)\n154:     }\n155: }\n156: ```\n157: \n158: ![two](figures/two.PNG)\n\n(End of file - total 158 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## 页面切换方式\n\nSwiper支持手指滑动和点击导航点两种方式切换页面，以下示例展示通过控制器切换页面的方法。\n\n <!-- run -->\n\n```cangjie\npackage ohos_app_cangjie_entry\nimport kit.ArkUI.*\nimport ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n\n@Entry\n@Component\nclass EntryView {\n    private var swiperBackgroundColors: Array<Color> = [Color.Blue, Color.Black, Color.Gray, Color.Green, Color.White, Color.Red]\n    private var swiperController: SwiperController = SwiperController();\n    @State var animationModeStr: Bool = false\n    @State var targetIndex: Int64 = 0\n    func build() {\n        Column(space: 5) {","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-layout-development-create-looping\\创建轮播Swiper\\页面切换方式_3more_9dc4c044.md","time":{"start":1782366297749,"end":1782366297760}},"id":"prt_efd4f5e3a001RwJHPSyi9ibYPW","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","messageID":"msg_efd4f16d4001SKgCELNFTYcv7p"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782366297843,"sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_RsvLZgtdBa8VjD9TdfjyVhgs","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-types\\基础类型定义\\enum_TextInputStyle_751a70d5.md","limit":120},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-types\\基础类型定义\\enum_TextInputStyle_751a70d5.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ## enum TextInputStyle\n2: \n3: ```cangjie\n4: public enum TextInputStyle <: Equatable<TextInputStyle> {\n5:     | Default\n6:     | Inline\n7:     | ...\n8: }\n9: ```\n10: \n11: **功能：** 表示输入风格。\n12: \n13: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n14: \n15: **起始版本：** 22\n16: \n17: **父类型：**\n18: \n19: - Equatable\\<[TextInputStyle](#enum-textinputstyle)>\n20: \n21: ### Default\n22: \n23: ```cangjie\n24: Default\n25: ```\n26: \n27: **功能：** 表示默认风格，光标宽1.5.vp，光标高度与文本选中底板高度和字体大小相关。\n28: \n29: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n30: \n31: **起始版本：** 22\n32: \n33: ### Inline\n34: \n35: ```cangjie\n36: Inline\n37: ```\n38: \n39: **功能：** 表示内联输入风格。文本选中底板高度与输入框高度相同。内联输入适用于需要明显区分编辑状态和非编辑状态的场景，如文件列表视图中的重命名。内联输入不支持`showError`属性，并且在内联模式下不支持拖入文本功能。\n40: \n41: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n42: \n43: **起始版本：** 22\n44: \n45: ### operator func ==(TextInputStyle)\n46: \n47: ```cangjie\n48: public operator func ==(other: TextInputStyle): Bool\n49: ```\n50: \n51: **功能：** 判断两个TextInputStyle枚举是否相等。\n52: \n53: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n54: \n55: **起始版本：** 22\n56: \n57: **参数：**\n58: \n59: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n60: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n61: |other|[TextInputStyle](#enum-textinputstyle)|是|-|要比较的另一个TextInputStyle枚举。|\n62: \n63: **返回值：**\n64: \n65: |类型|说明|\n66: |:----|:----|\n67: |Bool|如果两个枚举相等则返回true，否则返回false。|\n68: \n69: ### operator func !=(TextInputStyle)\n70: \n71: ```cangjie\n72: public operator func !=(other: TextInputStyle): Bool\n73: ```\n74: \n75: **功能：** 判断两个TextInputStyle枚举是否不相等。\n76: \n77: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n78: \n79: **起始版本：** 22\n80: \n81: **参数：**\n82: \n83: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n84: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n85: |other|[TextInputStyle](#enum-textinputstyle)|是|-|要比较的另一个TextInputStyle枚举。|\n86: \n87: **返回值：**\n88: \n89: |类型|说明|\n90: |:----|:----|\n91: |Bool|如果两个枚举不相等则返回true，否则返回false。|\n\n(End of file - total 91 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## enum TextInputStyle\n\n```cangjie\npublic enum TextInputStyle <: Equatable<TextInputStyle> {\n    | Default\n    | Inline\n    | ...\n}\n```\n\n**功能：** 表示输入风格。\n\n**系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n\n**起始版本：** 22\n\n**父类型：**\n\n- Equatable\\<[TextInputStyle](#enum-textinputstyle)>\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-types\\基础类型定义\\enum_TextInputStyle_751a70d5.md","time":{"start":1782366297835,"end":1782366297843}},"id":"prt_efd4f5e97001ChbiPfJiYX22WS","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","messageID":"msg_efd4f16d4001SKgCELNFTYcv7p"}}
