.ArkUI.Full\n95: \n96: **起始版本：** 22\n97: \n98: ### NewLine\n99: \n100: ```cangjie\n101: NewLine\n102: ```\n103: \n104: **功能：** 显示为换行样式。\n105: \n106: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n107: \n108: **起始版本：** 22\n109: \n110: ### operator func ==(EnterKeyType)\n111: \n112: ```cangjie\n113: public operator func ==(other: EnterKeyType): Bool\n114: ```\n115: \n116: **功能：** 判断两个EnterKeyType枚举是否相等。\n117: \n118: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n119: \n120: **起始版本：** 22\n\n(Showing lines 1-120 of 156. Use offset=121 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## enum EnterKeyType\n\n```cangjie\npublic enum EnterKeyType <: Equatable<EnterKeyType> {\n    | Go\n    | Search\n    | Send\n    | Next\n    | Done\n    | Previous\n    | NewLine\n    | ...\n}\n```\n\n**功能：** 表示键盘操作按钮的类型。\n\n**系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n\n**起始版本：** 22","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-types\\基础类型定义\\enum_EnterKeyType.md","time":{"start":1782366297921,"end":1782366297928}},"id":"prt_efd4f5eed001A5lxDt7so5Si35","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","messageID":"msg_efd4f16d4001SKgCELNFTYcv7p"}}
