{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782366328589,"sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_vFeCFqs2P9fWbfm5TEghqYOo","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-text-input-textinput\\TextInput\\基础类型定义_2more_3de06505.md","limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-text-input-textinput\\TextInput\\基础类型定义_2more_3de06505.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ## 基础类型定义\n2: \n3: ### class TextInputController\n4: \n5: ```cangjie\n6: public class TextInputController {\n7:     public init()\n8: }\n9: ```\n10: \n11: **功能：** TextInputController是TextInput组件的控制器，可以定义该类型的对象并绑定至TextInput组件，实现对TextInput组件的控制。\n12: \n13: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n14: \n15: **起始版本：** 22\n16: \n17: #### init()\n18: \n19: ```cangjie\n20: public init()\n21: ```\n22: \n23: **功能：** TextInputController的构造函数。\n24: \n25: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n26: \n27: **起始版本：** 22\n28: \n29: #### func caretPosition(?Int32)\n30: \n31: ```cangjie\n32: public func caretPosition(value: ?Int32): Unit\n33: ```\n34: \n35: **功能：** 设置插入光标的位置。\n36: \n37: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n38: \n39: **起始版本：** 22\n40: \n41: **参数：**\n42: \n43: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n44: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n45: |value|?Int32|是|-|光标位置。|\n46: \n47: #### func setTextSelection(?Int32, ?Int32, ?MenuPolicy)\n48: \n49: ```cangjie\n50: public func setTextSelection(selectionStart: ?Int32, selectionEnd: ?Int32, options!: ?MenuPolicy = None): Unit\n51: ```\n52: \n53: **功能：** 通过指定文本的起始和结束位置实现文本选择。\n54: \n55: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n56: \n57: **起始版本：** 22\n58: \n59: **参数：**\n60: \n61: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n62: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n63: |selectionStart|?Int32|是|-|选中文本的起始位置。|\n64: |selectionEnd|?Int32|是|-|选中文本的结束位置。|\n65: |options|?[MenuPolicy](./cj-common-types.md#enum-menupolicy)|否|None| **命名参数。** 文本选择的选项。<br>初始值：MenuPolicy.Default。|\n66: \n67: #### func stopEditing()\n68: \n69: ```cangjie\n70: public func stopEditing(): Unit\n71: ```\n72: \n73: **功能：** 退出编辑状态。\n74: \n75: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n76: \n77: **起始版本：** 22\n78: \n79: ## 示例代码\n80: \n81: <!--run-->\n82: \n83: ```cangjie\n84: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n85: import kit.ArkUI.*\n86: import ohos.hilog.*\n87: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n88: \n89: @Entry\n90: @Component\n91: class EntryView {\n92:     @State var text: String = ''\n93:     @State var passwordState: Bool = false\n94:     var controller: TextInputController = TextInputController()\n95: \n96:     func build() {\n97:     Column() {\n98:         TextInput(text: this.text, placeholder: 'input your word...', controller: this.controller)\n99:             .placeholderColor(Color.Gray)\n100:             .placeholderFont(size: 14, weight: FontWeight.W100)\n101:             .caretColor(Color.Blue)\n102:             .width(95.percent)\n103:             .height(40)\n104:             .margin(20)\n105:             .fontSize(14)\n106:             .fontColor(Color.Black)\n107:             .inputFilter('[a-z]', error: { info: String =>\n108:               Hilog.error(0, \"AppLogCj\", \"inputFilter error\")\n109:             })\n110:             .onChange({ value: String =>\n111:               this.text = value\n112:             })\n113:         Text(this.text)\n114:         Button('Set caretPosition 1')\n115:             .margin(15)\n116:             .onClick({ evt => \n117:                 // 将光标移动至第一个字符后\n118:                 this.controller.caretPosition(1)\n119:             })\n120:         // 内联风格输入框\n121:         TextInput( text: 'inline style' )\n122:             .width(95.percent)\n123:             .height(50)\n124:             .margin(20)\n125:             .borderRadius(0)\n126:             .style(TextInputStyle.Inline)\n127:         }.\n128:         width(100.percent)\n129:     }\n130: }\n131: ```\n132: \n133: ![textinput](figures/textinput.png)\n\n(End of file - total 133 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## 基础类型定义\n\n### class TextInputController\n\n```cangjie\npublic class TextInputController {\n    public init()\n}\n```\n\n**功能：** TextInputController是TextInput组件的控制器，可以定义该类型的对象并绑定至TextInput组件，实现对TextInput组件的控制。\n\n**系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n\n**起始版本：** 22\n\n#### init()\n\n```cangjie\npublic init()","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-text-input-textinput\\TextInput\\基础类型定义_2more_3de06505.md","time":{"start":1782366328582,"end":1782366328589}},"id":"prt_efd4fd630001cTca6CrBPqIaLy","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","messageID":"msg_efd4f6212001dWAaY5lcb9DCgY"}}
