md:\n  Line 9: ArkUI通过[自定义组件](../paradigm/cj-create-custom-components.md)的build()函数和[@Builder宏](../paradigm/cj-macro-builder.md)中的声明式UI描述语句构建相应的UI。在声明式描述语句中开发者除了使用系统组件外，还可以使用渲染控制语句来辅助UI的构建，这些渲染控制语句包括控制组件是否显示的条件渲染语句，基于数组数据快速生成组件的循环渲染语句，针对大数据量场景的数据懒加载语句，针对混合模式开发的组件渲染语句。\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-overview\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: 本目录专注于ArkUI框架中声明式UI构建的渲染控制机制。它详细阐述了开发者如何在自定义组件的`build()`函数及`@Builder`装饰器中，运用条件渲染、循环渲染、数据懒加载以及混合模式组件渲染等关键技术。文档不仅解释了这些控制语句的基本概念，还深入探讨了它们如何根据数据状态的变化动态生成或控制UI界面。特别地，它针对大数据量场景下的性能优化提供了指导，并支持混合开发模式的实现。该文档主要面向使用ArkUI进行声明式UI开发的工程师，要求读者已具备自定义组件和基础UI描述语句的相关背景知识，旨在帮助开发者构建更高效、响应更灵敏的用户界面。\r\n\n  Line 20: 本文档旨在概述ArkUI框架中声明式UI构建所使用的渲染控制语句及其基本概念。主要介绍了在自定义组件的build()函数和@Builder宏中，如何利用条件渲染、循环渲染、数据懒加载以及混合模式组件渲染等语句来辅助UI构建。核心要点在于掌握这些控制语句如何基于数据状态动态生成或控制UI组件，特别是针对大数据量场景的优化和混合开发模式的支持。文档面向使用ArkUI进行声明式UI开发的开发者，要求其具备自定义组件和基础UI描述语句的相关知识。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-overview\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: 本目录专注于ArkUI框架中声明式UI构建的渲染控制机制。它详细阐述了开发者如何在自定义组件的`build()`函数及`@Builder`装饰器中，运用条件渲染、循环渲染、数据懒加载以及混合模式组件渲染等关键技术。文档不仅解释了这些控制语句的基本概念，还深入探讨了它们如何根据数据状态的变化动态生成或控制UI界面。特别地，它针对大数据量场景下的性能优化提供了指导，并支持混合开发模式的实现。该文档主要面向使用ArkUI进行声明式UI开发的工程师，要求读者已具备自定义组件和基础UI描述语句的相关背景知识，旨...\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-foreach\\ForEach循环渲染\\非首次渲染_3more_f6798f42.md:\n  Line 74: @Builder\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-foreach\\ForEach循环渲染\\数据源数组项发生变化.md:\n  Line 27: @Builder\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\.overview.md:\n  Line 17: This directory focuses on rendering control mechanisms for declarative UI construction within the ArkUI framework. It details how developers can utilize key technologies such as conditional rendering, loop rendering, data lazy loading, and mixed-mode component rendering within custom component `build()` functions and `@Builder` decorators. The documentation explains the basic concepts of these control statements and delves into how they dynamically generate or control UI interfaces based on changes in data state. Specifically, it provides guidance on performance optimization for large data volume scenarios and supports the implementation of mixed development modes. This document is primarily intended for engineers using ArkUI for declarative UI development, requiring readers to have a background in custom components and basic UI description statements.\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-reusable\\Reusable宏组件复用\\限制条件.md:\n  Line 15:     // @Builder加上@Reusable编译报错，不适用于builder\r\n\n  Line 17:     @Builder\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-reusable\\Reusable宏组件复用\\.overview.md:\n  Line 21: 本文档旨在说明ArkUI仓颉开发中使用@Reusable宏时的限制条件与注意事项。主要涵盖混合工程支持情况、@Reusable的适用范围以及嵌套使用的潜在问题。关键信息包括：暂不支持混合工程；@Reusable仅适用于自定义组件，不可用于@Builder；严禁嵌套使用@Reusable，因为会导致内存增加、复用效率降低、生命周期方法无法成对调用及维护困难。该文档面向使用ArkUI仓颉语言进行应用开发的开发者，旨在帮助其正确使用组件复用功能以避免性能陷阱。\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builderparam\\BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数\\常见问题_8d5030fb.md:\n  Line 3: ### @BuilderParam宏初始化的值必须为@Builder\r\n\n  Line 5: 使用@State宏修饰的变量，给子组件@BuilderParam和ChildBuilder变量进行初始化，在编译时会输出报错信息。\r\n\n  Line 16: @Builder func globalBuilder() {\r\n\n  Line 33:     @BuilderParam var ChildBuilder: () -> Unit = globalBuilder;\r\n\n  Line 42: 使用全局的@Builder修饰的globalBuilder()给子组件@BuilderParam修饰的ChildBuilder变量进行初始化，编译时没有报错，功能正常。\r\n\n  Line 53: @Builder func globalBuilder() {\r\n\n  Line 68:     @BuilderParam var ChildBuilder: () -> Unit = globalBuilder;\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builderparam\\BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数\\使用场景.md:\n  Line 5: @BuilderParam修饰的方法可以是有参数和无参数的两种形式，需与指向的@Builder方法类型匹配。\r\n\n  Line 21: @Builder func overBuilder(tmp: Tmp) {\r\n\n  Line 32:     @BuilderParam var customBuilderParam: () -> Unit\r\n\n  Line 34:     @BuilderParam var customOverBuilderParam: (Tmp) -> Unit = overBuilder\r\n\n  Line 38:             this.customBuilderParam()\r\n\n  Line 39:             this.customOverBuilderParam(Tmp(\"  global Builder label\"))\r\n\n  Line 49:     @Builder func componentBuilder() {\r\n\n  Line 56:             Child(customBuilderParam: this.componentBuilder)\r\n\n  Line 66: ### 使用全局和父组件@Builder初始化@BuilderParam\r\n\n  Line 68: 在自定义组件中，使用@BuilderParam修饰的变量接收来自父组件通过@Builder传递的内容进行初始化。\r\n\n  Line 77: @Builder func customBuilder() {}\r\n\n  Line 83:     @BuilderParam var customBuilderParam: () -> Unit = customBuilder\r\n\n  Line 87:             this.customBuilderParam()\r\n\n  Line 94: @Builder func overBuilder() {\r\n\n  Line 107:     @Builder func componentBuilder() {\r\n\n  Line 120:                 // 把this.componentBuilder传给子组件ChildPage的@BuilderParam customBuilderParam。\r\n\n  Line 121:                 customBuilderParam: this.componentBuilder\r\n\n  Line 130:             // 把全局overBuilder传给子组件ChildPage的@BuilderParam customBuilderParam，所以展示的内容为\"Hello World\"。\r\n\n  Line 131:             customBuilderParam: overBuilder\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builderparam\\BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数\\BuilderParam宏引用Bu_3more_93460a8d.md:\n  Line 1: # @BuilderParam宏：引用@Builder函数\r\n\n  Line 9: 当开发者创建了自定义组件，并想对该组件添加特定功能，例如想在某一个指定的自定义组件中添加一个点击跳转操作，此时若直接在组件内嵌入事件方法，将会导致所有该自定义组件的实例都增加了功能。为解决此问题，ArkUI引入了@BuilderParam宏，@BuilderParam用来修饰指向@Builder方法的变量（@BuilderParam是用来承接@Builder函数的）。开发者可以在初始化自定义组件时，使用不同的方式（如：参数修改、父组件初始化等）对@BuilderParam修饰的自定义构建函数进行传参赋值，在自定义组件内部通过调用@BuilderParam为组件增加特定的功能。该宏用于声明任意UI描述的一个元素，类似slot占位符。\r\n\n  Line 11: 在阅读本文档前，建议提前阅读：[@Builder](./cj-macro-builder.md)。\r\n\n  Line 15: ### 初始化@BuilderParam修饰的方法\r\n\n  Line 17: @BuilderParam修饰的方法只能被自定义构建函数（@Builder修饰的方法）初始化。\r\n\n  Line 19: 使用全局的自定义构建函数，在本地初始化@BuilderParam。\r\n\n  Line 28: @Builder func overBuilder() {}\r\n\n  Line 32:     // 使用全局自定义构建函数初始化@BuilderParam\r\n\n  Line 33:     @BuilderParam var customOverBuilderParam: () -> Unit = overBuilder\r\n\n  Line 41: 使用@BuilderParam有如下限制：\r\n\n  Line 43: - 所修饰的变量只能使用@Builder函数进行初始化。\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builderparam\\BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数\\.overview.md:\n  Line 1: # BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数\r\n\n  Line 3: 本目录包含关于ArkUI框架中@BuilderParam宏的详细文档，重点讲解如何通过引用@Builder函数实现类似插槽的动态UI构建。内容涵盖宏的基本用法、限制条件、参数传递规则及常见错误处理。核心关键词包括ArkUI、@BuilderParam、@Builder、仓颉语言、动态UI。文档适合具备仓颉语言基础的ArkUI开发者阅读，旨在帮助开发者掌握组件复用与灵活构建的技巧。\r\n\n  Line 7: - 想了解@BuilderParam宏的基本概念、核心用法及限制条件？ → BuilderParam宏引用Bu_3more_93460a8d.md\r\n\n  Line 13: ### BuilderParam宏引用Bu_3more_93460a8d.md\r\n\n  Line 14: 本文档介绍了ArkUI中的@BuilderParam宏，旨在解决自定义组件实例化时动态添加特定功能的问题，通过引用@Builder函数实现类似插槽的占位符功能。主要涵盖宏使用说明（如使用全局@Builder函数初始化）及限制条件（包括变量类型、初始化规则、作用域及可变性要求）。核心要点包括：@BuilderParam修饰的变量必须是显式标注的函数类型且返回Unit，仅限类成员变量，只能由@Builder函数初始化，用于声明UI描述元素。面向使用仓颉语言的ArkUI开发者，需具备@Builder基础知识，适用于需要灵活构建自定义组件UI的场景。\r\n\n  Line 17: 本文档旨在阐述ArkUI框架中@BuilderParam装饰器的具体应用场景及参数传递规则。文档主要涵盖参数初始化组件、以及利用全局和父组件@Builder初始化@BuilderParam两个核心部分。关键信息包括@BuilderParam支持有参和无参形式，且类型必须与目标@Builder方法匹配；同时展示了子组件如何通过该装饰器接收并执行父组件或全局作用域的构建函数。本文档适合具备仓颉语言基础的开发者阅读，旨在指导其实现组件的灵活复用与动态UI构建。\r\n\n  Line 20: 本文档旨在解答ArkUI开发中关于@BuilderParam宏初始化的常见问题。文档通过反例与正例对比，详细阐述了在仓颉语言中，子组件的@BuilderParam变量不能由父组件的@State变量初始化，否则会导致编译报错。正确的做法是使用全局的@Builder函数进行赋值。该文档适合ArkUI及仓颉语言开发者阅读，帮助其理解组件传参规则并避免编译错误。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builderparam\\BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: 本目录包含关于ArkUI框架中@BuilderParam宏的详细文档，重点讲解如何通过引用@Builder函数实现类似插槽的动态UI构建。内容涵盖宏的基本用法、限制条件、参数传递规则及常见错误处理。核心关键词包括ArkUI、@BuilderParam、@Builder、仓颉语言、动态UI。文档适合具备仓颉语言基础的ArkUI开发者阅读，旨在帮助开发者掌握组件复用与灵活构建的技巧。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builderparam\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: This directory provides an in-depth exploration of the `cj-macro-builderparam` module, a specialized component within the ArkUI framework designed for the Cangjie programming language. The primary focus of this documentation is the `@BuilderParam` macro, a powerful feature that facilitates dynamic UI construction by allowing developers to reference `@Builder` functions. This mechanism mimics the functionality of slots found in other web frameworks, enabling highly reusable and flexible component architectures. The content covers a wide range of essential topics, including the fundamental usage of the macro, specific restrictions that developers must observe, the rules governing parameter passing, and effective methods for handling common errors. By mastering these concepts, developers can significantly improve the modularity of their code. This resource is specifically curated for ArkUI developers who possess a working knowledge of the Cangjie language and are seeking to advance their expertise in creating sophisticated, dynamic user interfaces.\r\n\n  Line 9: *   Understand the basics of `@BuilderParam` and `@Builder`? → See [1] BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数/\r\n\n  Line 10: *   Learn about parameter passing and restrictions? → See [1] BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数/\r\n\n  Line 11: *   Troubleshoot common errors in dynamic UI? → See [1] BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数/\r\n\n  Line 15: ### [1] BuilderParam宏引用Builder函数/\r\n\n  Line 17: This directory contains detailed documentation about the @BuilderParam macro in the ArkUI framework, focusing on how to implement dynamic UI construction similar to slots by referencing @Builder functions. Content covers basic usage, restrictions, parameter passing rules, and common error handling. Core keywords include ArkUI, @BuilderParam, @Builder, Cangjie language, dynamic UI. The documentation is suitable for ArkUI developers with a foundation in the Cangjie language, aiming to help developers master component reuse and flexible construction techniques.\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builderparam\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: This directory provides an in-depth exploration of the `cj-macro-builderparam` module, a specialized component within the ArkUI framework designed for the Cangjie programming language. The primary focus of this documentation is the `@BuilderParam` macro...\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builder\\Builder宏自定义构建函数\\参数传递规则_2more_10609097.md:\n  Line 7: - 在@Builder修饰的函数内部，不允许改变参数值。\r\n\n  Line 9: - @Builder内UI语法遵循[UI语法规则](./cj-create-custom-components.md)。\r\n\n  Line 15: 调用@Builder修饰的函数默认按值传递。当传递的参数为状态变量时，状态变量的改变不会引起@Builder方法内的UI刷新。所以当使用状态变量的时候，推荐使用[按引用传递](#按引用传递参数)。\r\n\n  Line 25: @Builder\r\n\n  Line 47: 按引用传递参数时，传递的参数可为状态变量，且状态变量的改变会引起@Builder方法内的UI刷新。\r\n\n  Line 62: @Builder\r\n\n  Line 92: @Builder通过按引用传递的方式传入参数，才会触发动态渲染UI。请参考[按引用传递参数](#按引用传递参数)。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\paradigm\\cj-macro-builder\\Builder宏自定义构建函数\\使用场景\\自定义组件内使用自定义构建函数_3more_9876ffa8.md:\n  Line 3: 创建私有的@Builder方法，在Column里面使用this.builder()方式调用，通过aboutToAppear生命周期函数和按钮的点击事件改变builder_value的内容，实现动态渲染UI。\r\n\n  Li