seCustomDialog(customdialogId)\r\n\n  Line 87:                     evt => getUIContext().getPromptAction().openCustomDialog(\r\n\n  Line 123:                     evt => getUIContext().getPromptAction().closeCustomDialog(customdialogId)\r\n\n  Line 133:                             evt => getUIContext().getPromptAction().openCustomDialog(\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-uicontext-custom-dialog\\不依赖UI组件的全局自定义弹出框openCustomDialog\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: 本目录主要介绍在HarmonyOS开发中，使用Cangjie语言通过`openCustomDialog` API实现不依赖UI组件的全局自定义弹出框。内容涵盖了如何解决传统`CustomDialogController`无法动态创建和刷新的问题，详细讲解了`CustomDialogOptions`配置、生命周期回调、ID管理以及UI解耦方案。此外，还提供了完整的代码示例，演示如何通过`UIContext`和`PromptAction`管理弹窗。适合具备ArkUI和Cangjie基础的开发者学习，旨在提供更灵活的弹窗封装与管理能力。\r\n\n  Line 17: 这份文档提供了一个完整的Cangjie语言代码示例，旨在演示如何在HarmonyOS应用中通过UIContext的PromptAction来管理自定义对话框。文档涵盖了EntryView组件的定义、使用@Builder装饰器构建对话框内容，以及在build方法中通过按钮事件触发openCustomDialog和closeCustomDialog的实现细节。关键点在于展示了如何利用bind函数绑定构建器，并使用CustomDialogOptions进行配置。该示例适合具备Cangjie基础的开发者，用于学习UI交互和弹窗控制逻辑。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-uicontext-custom-dialog\\不依赖UI组件的全局自定义弹出框openCustomDialog\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: 本目录主要介绍在HarmonyOS开发中，使用Cangjie语言通过`openCustomDialog` API实现不依赖UI组件的全局自定义弹出框。内容涵盖了如何解决传统`CustomDialogController`无法动态创建和刷新的问题，详细讲解了`CustomDialogOptions`配置、生命周期回调、ID管理以及UI解耦方案。此外，还提供了完整的代码示例，演示如何通过`UIContext`和`PromptAction`管理弹窗。适合具备ArkUI和Cangjie基础的开发者学习，旨在提...\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-uicontext-custom-dialog\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: This directory serves as a specialized technical resource for HarmonyOS developers working with the Cangjie language, focusing on the implementation of advanced dialog mechanisms. It specifically addresses the creation of global custom popups that function independently of underlying UI components using the `openCustomDialog` API. The core objective is to resolve architectural limitations found in the traditional `CustomDialogController`, particularly its lack of support for dynamic instantiation and real-time content refreshing. By exploring `CustomDialogOptions`, lifecycle callbacks, and UI decoupling strategies via `UIContext` and `PromptAction`, this guide provides the necessary tools for building scalable user interfaces. It is intended for developers with a solid grasp of ArkUI and Cangjie who are seeking to implement more flexible and powerful dialog management solutions in their projects.\r\n\n  Line 15: The content covers a wide array of technical details, including the precise configuration of `CustomDialogOptions` to customize appearance and behavior, the management of lifecycle callbacks to handle events properly, and ID management to track dialog instances efficiently. A significant portion of the guide is dedicated to the UI decoupling scheme, demonstrating how to use `UIContext` and `PromptAction` to manage popups in a global context. Through the provision of complete, executable code examples, developers can learn how to apply these concepts practically. This section is particularly valuable for those with existing knowledge of ArkUI and Cangjie who aim to refine their application architecture and improve user experience through better dialog control.\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-fixes-style-dialog\\固定样式弹出框\\固定样式弹出框_4more_4d358bcd.md:\n  Line 13: - 操作菜单（showActionMenu）、对话框（showDialog）需先使用[getPromptAction](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-uicontext.md#func-getpromptaction)方法获取到PromptAction对象，再通过该对象调用对应方法。\r\n\n  Line 19: 操作菜单通过[UIContext](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-uicontext.md#class-uicontext)中的[getPromptAction](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-uicontext.md#func-getpromptaction)方法获取到PromptAction对象，支持在回调或开发者自定义类中使用。\r\n\n  Line 47:                     getUIContext().getPromptAction().showActionMenu(ActionMenuOptions(title: \"showActionMenu Title Info\", buttons: buttons),\r\n\n  Line 69: 对话框通过[getPromptAction](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-uicontext.md#func-getpromptaction)方法获取到PromptAction对象，支持在回调或开发者自定义类中使用。\r\n\n  Line 94:                     getUIContext().getPromptAction().showDialog(\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-fixes-style-dialog\\固定样式弹出框\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: 本目录汇集了HarmonyOS ArkUI框架下关于固定样式弹出框的开发文档，主要使用仓颉语言编写。内容涵盖了列表选择弹窗、警告弹窗以及通用固定样式弹窗的实现与自定义。核心知识点包括UIContext和PromptAction接口的使用、样式布局配置、非对称过渡动效以及异步回调处理。这些文档适合正在使用仓颉语言开发HarmonyOS应用的开发者，旨在指导其构建具有丰富交互效果和标准化的弹窗组件。\r\n\n  Line 19: 本文档是HarmonyOS ArkUI开发指南，介绍了固定样式弹出框的使用方法，旨在通过预设布局简化开发。文档主要涵盖使用约束、操作菜单和对话框三个部分。核心内容包括必须通过getPromptAction获取PromptAction对象来调用方法，以及如何设置非模态弹窗。文档提供了详细的Cangjie语言代码示例，演示了showActionMenu和showDialog的创建与异步回调处理。主要面向使用Cangjie语言的HarmonyOS开发者，帮助他们快速实现标准化的弹窗交互功能。\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-fixes-style-dialog\\固定样式弹出框\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: 本目录汇集了HarmonyOS ArkUI框架下关于固定样式弹出框的开发文档，主要使用仓颉语言编写。内容涵盖了列表选择弹窗、警告弹窗以及通用固定样式弹窗的实现与自定义。核心知识点包括UIContext和PromptAction接口的使用、样式布局配置、非对称过渡动效以及异步回调处理。这些文档适合正在使用仓颉语言开发HarmonyOS应用的开发者，旨在指导其构建具有丰富交互效果和标准化的弹窗组件。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-fixes-style-dialog\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: This directory serves as a comprehensive resource for developers working with the HarmonyOS ArkUI framework and the Cangjie programming language. It focuses specifically on the creation and management of fixed-style dialogs, which are essential for standardized user interactions in mobile applications. The documentation covers a range of dialog types, including list selection and alert dialogs, providing the necessary guidance to implement them effectively. Key technical areas explored include the utilization of UIContext and PromptAction interfaces, configuring style layouts, implementing asymmetric transition animations, and handling asynchronous callbacks. This collection is ideal for developers seeking to enhance their HarmonyOS applications with polished, interactive, and standardized dialog components using modern Cangjie language features.\r\n\n  Line 17: The core of the documentation focuses on mastering the UIContext and PromptAction interfaces, which are fundamental for managing dialog display and behavior in ArkUI. Beyond basic implementation, the text guides developers through complex style layout configurations, ensuring that dialogs adhere to specific design guidelines. A significant portion of the content is dedicated to advanced visual and functional features, such as implementing asymmetric transition animations that provide a unique user experience, and managing asynchronous callbacks to handle user inputs without blocking the main thread. These documents are highly suitable for developers who are adopting the Cangjie language for their HarmonyOS projects, providing the necessary technical depth to build standardized, highly interactive, and visually appealing dialog components.\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-dialog-overview\\cj-dialog-overview.md:\n  Line 33: | [即时反馈（Toast）](cj-create-toast.md) | 当需要在一个小的窗口中提供用户当前操作的简单反馈时，例如提示文件保存成功等，应用优先考虑使用此弹窗。|\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-dialog-overview\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: 本目录包含CJ框架弹窗系统的核心概览文档，专注于为开发者提供全面的弹窗组件选择与使用指南。文档深入探讨了模态与非模态弹窗的交互逻辑差异，详细介绍了Dialog、Menu、Popup及Toast等关键组件的适用场景。同时，涵盖了弹窗的层级管理（后进先出原则）以及移动端开发中子窗尺寸的严格限制。该资料主要面向应用开发者，旨在帮助其理解弹窗类型转换机制及使用边界，从而构建符合规范且用户体验良好的应用界面。\r\n\n  Line 9:     - 查阅Dialog、Menu、Popup、Toast的具体应用场景 → cj-dialog-overview.md\r\n\n  Line 17: 本文档是CJ框架弹窗组件的权威指南，旨在帮助开发者根据具体的交互需求精准选择合适的弹窗类型。文档首先详细区分了模态弹窗（具有强交互性，要求用户必须响应）与非模态弹窗（具有弱交互性，通常会自动消失），并列举了Dialog、Menu、Popup、Toast等组件的具体应用场景，为开发者提供了清晰的选型依据。此外，文档还深入说明了弹窗的层级堆叠规则，即遵循后进先出（LIFO）的原则，以及移动端开发中子窗无法超出主窗口的规格约束。该指南特别适合应用开发者阅读，提供了关于弹窗类型转换及使用限制的关键信息，确保开发出的界面既符合框架规范又能满足用户交互预期。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-dialog-overview\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: 本目录包含CJ框架弹窗系统的核心概览文档，专注于为开发者提供全面的弹窗组件选择与使用指南。文档深入探讨了模态与非模态弹窗的交互逻辑差异，详细介绍了Dialog、Menu、Popup及Toast等关键组件的适用场景。同时，涵盖了弹窗的层级管理（后进先出原则）以及移动端开发中子窗尺寸的严格限制。该资料主要面向应用开发者，旨在帮助其理解弹窗类型转换机制及使用边界，从而构建符合规范且用户体验良好的应用界面。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-create-toast\\即时反馈Toast\\即时反馈模式对比_2more_bd07012b.md:\n  Line 5: 在TopMost类型的Toast显示前，会创建一个全屏大小的子窗（终端上子窗大小和主窗大小一致），然后在该子窗上计算Toast的布局位置，最后显示在该子窗上。具体和Default模式Toast的差异如下：\r\n\n  Line 29:                 Text(\"Default类型Toast\")\r\n\n  Line 35:                 getUIContext().getPromptAction().showToast(\r\n\n  Line 36:                         ShowToastOptions(\r\n\n  Line 40:                             showMode: ToastShowMode.Default\r\n\n  Line 51:                 Text(\"TopMost类型Toast\")\r\n\n  Line 57:                 getUIContext().getPromptAction().showToast(\r\n\n  Line 58:                         ShowToastOptions(\r\n\n  Line 62:                             showMode: ToastShowMode.TopMost\r\n\n  Line 98:                     getUIContext().getPromptAction().showToast(\r\n\n  Line 99:                         ShowToastOptions(\r\n\n  Line 111: ![image](figures/UIToast1.gif)\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-create-toast\\即时反馈Toast\\即时反馈Toast_2more_a8241700.md:\n  Line 1: # 即时反馈（Toast）\r\n\n  Line 9: 即时反馈（Toast）是一种临时性的消息提示框，用于向用户显示简短的操作反馈或状态信息。​它通常在屏幕的底部或顶部短暂弹出，随后在一段时间后自动消失。即时反馈的主要目的是提供简洁、不打扰的信息反馈，避免干扰用户当前的操作流程。\r\n\n  Line 11: 可以通过使用[UIContext](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-uicontext.md)中的[getPromptAction](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-uicontext.md#func-getpromptaction)方法获取当前UI上下文关联的[PromptAction](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-promptaction.md)对象，再通过该对象调用[showToast](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-promptaction.md#func-showtoastshowtoastoptions)创建并显示文本提示框。\r\n\n  Line 15: > 为了安全考虑，例如Toast恶意遮挡其他页面，Toast只能显示在当前的UI实例中，应用退出后，不会单独显示在桌面上。\r\n\n  Line 25:    Toast控件的文本应该清晰可读，字体大小和颜色应该与应用程序的主题相符。除此之外，即时反馈控件本身不应该包含任何可交互的元素，如按钮或链接。\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-create-toast\\即时反馈Toast\\.overview.md:\n  Line 1: # 即时反馈Toast\r\n\n  Line 3: 本目录包含关于HarmonyOS应用开发中即时反馈组件（Toast）的详细指南。内容涵盖了Toast组件的概念定义、基于UIContext和PromptAction接口的实现方式，以及ArkUI中Default与TopMost两种显示模式的对比分析。文档重点介绍了组件的使用规范、显示层级、软键盘避让机制及Cangjie语言实现示例。适合HarmonyOS及ArkUI应用开发者阅读，旨在帮助开发者掌握轻量级提示框的开发技巧，优化用户交互体验。\r\n\n  Line 7: - 想要了解Toast组件的概念、实现方式及使用规范 → 即时反馈Toast_2more_a8241700.md\r\n\n  Line 12: ### 即时反馈Toast_2more_a8241700.md 即时反馈Toast_2more_a8241700.md\r\n\n  Line 13: 本文档介绍即时反馈组件的概念、实现方式及使用建议，指导开发者利用轻量级提示框提供操作反馈。涵盖组件定义、通过UIContext和PromptAction接口的实现路径，以及关于弹出场景、文本密度和显示位置的规范。关键点包括Toast仅限当前UI实例显示、无交互元素、时长不超过3秒、字体最大放大2倍，且应避免频繁弹出和遮挡其他内容。面向HarmonyOS应用开发者，属于开发指南，旨在优化用户交互体验。\r\n\n  Line 16: 本文档对比了ArkUI中即时反馈的Default和TopMost两种显示模式，并提供了Cangjie语言的实现示例。内容涵盖TopMost模式的子窗机制、与Default模式在层级和软键盘避让方面的详细对比表，以及创建Toast的代码演示。关键差异在于TopMost会创建全屏子窗且层级较高，仅在遮挡时避让软键盘（保持80.vp间距），而Default模式始终位于主窗内。该文档适用于需要实现短时自动消失提示框的ArkUI开发者，需具备Cangjie基础。关键词：ArkUI, Cangjie, Toast, TopMost, 软键盘避让, 窗口层级。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-create-toast\\即时反馈Toast\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: 本目录包含关于HarmonyOS应用开发中即时反馈组件（Toast）的详细指南。内容涵盖了Toast组件的概念定义、基于UIContext和PromptAction接口的实现方式，以及ArkUI中Default与TopMost两种显示模式的对比分析。文档重点介绍了组件的使用规范、显示层级、软键盘避让机制及Cangjie语言实现示例。适合HarmonyOS及ArkUI应用开发者阅读，旨在帮助开发者掌握轻量级提示框的开发技巧，优化用户交互体验。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-create-toast\\.overview.md:\n  Line 3: This directory functions as a comprehensive technical repository for developers utilizing the Cangjie language within the HarmonyOS ecosystem, specifically targeting the creation and management of Toast components. It provides an in-depth look at the mechanisms required to build lightweight, instant feedback systems that are vital for modern mobile user interfaces. The guide explores the architectural foundations involving UIContext and PromptAction, offering detailed insights into how these interfaces facilitate the generation of prompts. Furthermore, it delves into the visual and behavioral nuances of Toasts, including display modes, layer management, and interaction with system elements like the soft keyboard. This material is highly suitable for HarmonyOS and ArkUI developers who aim to elevate their application's responsiveness and user interaction quality through the effective deployment of lightweight notifications and prompt systems.\r\n\n  Line 9: - Want to understand the core concepts and definitions of the Toast component? → Go to `即时反馈Toast/`\r\n\n  Line 10: - Need to know how to implement Toasts using UIContext and PromptAction interfaces? → Go to `即时反馈Toast/`\r\n\n  Line 11: - Looking for a comparison between Default and TopMost display modes? → Go to `即时反馈Toast/`\r\n\n  Line 12: - Want to see Cangjie code examples and learn about soft keyboard avoidance? → Go to `即时反馈Toast/`\r\n\n  Line 16: ### 即时反馈Toast/\r\n\n  Line 18: This directory contains a detailed and structured guide regarding the \"Instant Feedback Toast\" component, which is a pivotal element in HarmonyOS application development. The documentation is designed to provide a holistic understanding of Toasts, starting from their basic concept definition to their role in enhancing user engagement through immediate feedback loops.\r\n\n  Line 20: The guide provides a deep dive into the technical implementati