r func ==(other: InputType): Bool\n88: ```\n89: \n90: **功能：** 判断两个InputType枚举是否相等。\n91: \n92: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n93: \n94: **起始版本：** 22\n95: \n96: **参数：**\n97: \n98: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n99: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n100: |other|[InputType](#enum-inputtype)|是|-|要比较的另一个InputType枚举。|\n101: \n102: **返回值：**\n103: \n104: |类型|说明|\n105: |:----|:----|\n106: |Bool|如果两个枚举相等则返回true，否则返回false。|\n107: \n108: ### operator func !=(InputType)\n109: \n110: ```cangjie\n111: public operator func !=(other: InputType): Bool\n112: ```\n113: \n114: **功能：** 判断两个InputType枚举是否不相等。\n115: \n116: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n117: \n118: **起始版本：** 22\n119: \n120: **参数：**\n\n(Showing lines 1-120 of 130. Use offset=121 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## enum InputType\n\n```cangjie\npublic enum InputType <: Equatable<InputType> {\n    | Normal\n    | Number\n    | Email\n    | Password\n    | PhoneNumber\n    | ...\n}\n```\n\n**功能：** 表示输入框的类型。\n\n**系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full\n\n**起始版本：** 22\n\n**父类型：**","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-types\\基础类型定义\\enum_InputType.md","time":{"start":1782366905049,"end":1782366905058}},"id":"prt_efd58a284001D3e3Ce6QxxWy0h","sessionID":"ses_102b4b020ffezHsYsEmnxMB0zX","messageID":"msg_efd56b148001M84KX7jnbIxxOd"}}
